quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  72,1,"Qul oohiya ilayya annahu istamaAAanafarun mina aljinni faqaloo inna samiAAnaqur-anan AAajaba"
  72,2,"Yahdee ila arrushdi faamannabihi walan nushrika birabbina ahada"
  72,3,"Waannahu taAAala jaddu rabbinama ittakhatha sahibatan wala walada"
  72,4,"Waannahu kana yaqoolu safeehunaAAala Allahi shatata"
  72,5,"Waanna thanannaan lan taqoola al-insu waljinnu AAala Allahikathiba"
  72,6,"Waannahu kana rijalun minaal-insi yaAAoothoona birijalin mina aljinni fazadoohumrahaqa"
  72,7,"Waannahum thannoo kama thanantuman lan yabAAatha Allahu ahada"
  72,8,"Waanna lamasna assamaafawajadnaha muli-at harasan shadeedanwashuhuba"
  72,9,"Waanna kunna naqAAudu minhamaqaAAida lissamAAi faman yastamiAAi al-anayajid lahu shihaban rasada"
  72,10,"Waanna la nadree asharrunoreeda biman fee al-ardi am arada bihim rabbuhumrashada"
  72,11,"Waanna minna assalihoonawaminna doona thalika kunna tara-iqaqidada"
  72,12,"Wanna thanannaan lan nuAAjiza Allaha fee al-ardi walan nuAAjizahuharaba"
  72,13,"Waanna lamma samiAAnaalhuda amanna bihi faman yu/min birabbihifala yakhafu bakhsan wala rahaqa"
